data.title: Halo Hair Extensions Chestnut Flash Brown
data.meta_description: Add gorgeous volume & length to your hair with our Chestnut Flash Brown Halo Hair Extensions - Pure Diamonds Line. With incredible silkiness & smoothness!
data.text:
Details

Hallo- Extensions - Pure Diamonds Line

Rubin Extensions presents the revolutionary hair extension - Diamond Silk Line!

With our Diamond Set of Halo Hair Extensions, your hair will have volume all over (double drawn): it is a set that is unparalleled. You won't find a better hair extension anywhere! Enjoy great volume and wonderfully long hair thanks to this fast, uncomplicated method of lengthening your own hair.

Only the finest, smoothest hair is used, creating a comfortable feeling. Each package contains high-quality, Slavic human hair in Remy quality.

Halo Hair Extensions Quality

Finest Slavic Remy Human Hair

Remy Hair is always of high quality and the ideal hair for making human hair extensions. But only the very best quality is used in our HALO-HAIR EXTENSIONS DIAMOND LINE. We hand select the best Slavic human hair for this hair grade. Furthermore, our tangle-FREE formula protects the hair from tangling so that you can enjoy your top-quality extensions made from 100% human hair for many months. You can find out more about the quality of our human hair extensions in our information section!

Hair Extension Accessories and Care Line

Just like your real hair, hair extensions require care and attention to keep them looking their best. After all, our extensions are made from 100% human hair. Caring for your hair extensions will ensure they keep looking their best and last for longer. This is why we created our own exclusive line of accessories and hair extension care products, specially formulated to work with our line of premium remy hair extensions.

Our extensionsshampoo and conditioner are a great place to start. For everyday styling and to maintain a silky smooth look, try our Hair Extensions Spray Conditioner will help protect and nourish your hair. For more information on how to properly care for your new human hair extensions, please refer to our hair care instructions. We also provide all the accessories you need to maintain your hair extensions including replacement tapes and clips.
